description: Fusing authentic Spanish and Mexican traditions for great Latin food, El Orgullo Latino Kitchen brings delicious fare to the streets of Miami. Try the fish tacos, tacos guisados, or something completely different, but don't pass this tasty truck by! Tacos, loaded quesadillas and burritos, fajita wraps, Mexican tostadas, special sauced ribs, rice, empanadas, fresh made salsas, their signature chipotle sauce, plantain cups, and chimichurri steak sandwiches are a few more of the the top hits. This Latin kitchen is run by two cooks who put the magic in the seasoning following their country roots. Authentic food freshly made guaranteed!
name: El Orgullo Latino Kitchen
